column5: Well it could have been but I might have ate the first one.  Caught this when I was out with TEP on Monday in Cook's Bay.
Looks like someone missed a spot with the Rapala sissors.....oh ya there's no slot size for perch!
LOL   never hurts to have a little extra piece of tail
Uh oh, the perch have been cross breeding with all the beta's that are dropped into Kempenfelt Bay
Skud, please pass along best fishes to Mr. Christensen,  whatever the heck his name is .  I dunno.  TEP is a cool dood.
You know douG........ I do have internet access. I can see what you have been up to....  Happy New Year!
